						               													<description>HALVES is a word game for the ruthless!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At home, the office, band practice, in the bar or on a plane (where this game was conceived!) bring your friends together and find out who is the wordiest of all.  &amp;#10;Be careful though, winning cards is the easy bit, staying in the lead is where things get complicated.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To win the game, simply Guess the word on your opponent&amp;rsquo;s card to win points. Be the player with the most points at the end of the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The active player must choose a word from one card in their hand for their opponents to try and guess. The colour behind the chosen word dictates the game type for the round:&amp;#10;- Yellow is CATEGORIES, &amp;#10;- Blue is RHYMES WITH,&amp;#10;- Red is PERFECT PAIRS.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The active player must think of a clue for their word. Then they announce the game type and their clue to all players who have 30 seconds to guess it.&amp;#10;Any cards a player has won from a previous round is at risk from TRAP cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Guess, Swap, Bluff or Steal your way to put points on the table and be the envy of all your friends and family!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Created by Carter &amp;amp; Richardson the same minds that make up your favourite punk rock and roll band The Rattlesnakes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
